lezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60 WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: How to improve defensive skills</span><hr size=1> Tower of Frozen Shadow, 2nd level trap.<br>
<br>
As you zone into 2nd floor look to the right of the librarian area, adjacent to the first row of shelves.  You will see what looks like a brown, wooden table top sitting on the floor.  That is a trap which hit me for 31dmg max, and gives some incredible defense skill points over a short time.  Or, you could just sense traps and walk right to it.<br>
<br>
On this trap, you are behind all mobs or out of aggro range, so you are set with sneak.  It's a fantastic, easy, fast and safe way to get your defense maxed.  I had the fastest luck repeatedly sitting down on it v/s walking on/off.<br>
<br>
-Hurk of Luclin <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousetrainingstudioqafornewbies.showPrevMessage?topicID=12621.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousetrainingstudioqafornewbies.showNextMessage?topicID=12621.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousetrainingstudioqafornewbies.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=12621.topic&index=26><img src=http://www.thesafehouse.org/images/reply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousetrainingstudioqafornewbies.emailToFriend?topicID=12621.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousetrainingstudioqafornewbies.threadControl?topicID=12621.topic><img src=http://www.thesafehouse.org/images/dagger.jpg border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousetrainingstudioqafornewbies.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=12621.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousetrainingstudioqafornewbies.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=12621.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub35.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="thesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion">Main Lounge<option value="thesafehousecontractsbountiesjobsquestsetc">News Bulletin<option value="thesafehous